#include <stdio.h>
#include <vector>
#include <algorithm>
using namespace std;
int main()
{
	int T,i,count[110],n,num,ans;
	vector<int> k;
	scanf("%d",&T);
	while(T--)
	{
		k.clear();
		for(i=0;i<110;i++)
		{
			count[i] = 0;
		}
		scanf("%d",&n);
		while(n--)
		{
			scanf("%d",&num);
			k.push_back(num);
			count[num]++;
		}
		sort(k.begin(),k.end());
		for(i=0;i<k.size();i++)
		{
			if(count[k[i]] == 1)
			{
				ans = k[i];
				break;
			}
		}
		printf("%d\n",ans);
	}
	return 0;
}
